description:
Every week Elder Wilson delivers a special biblical message to every Seventh-day Adventist in the world. This week the message appeals to all of us to continue proclaiming the 3 angels' messages through this crisis. Elder Wilson also reminds us of the power of prayer during a crisis.

Please respond to this message in the comments. 

00:00 Greeting
01:30 Ted Wilson's sermon
05:19 A call from the pastor
05:34 Ted Wilson's Prayer
